{"tid":573101,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"買左Razer個Raiju手制喊出黎","createTime":"2018-02-26T06:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T09:51:07.000Z","uid":74044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c53c4609c52089a7118b97b7b44c20ac0ba2ec00","tid":573101,"uid":74044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T06:49:41.000Z","msg":"PS4手制壞左，諗住買翻個靚野黎用下<br />\n睇過N牌同R牌兩個，R牌個靜音功能制十分適合我，睇過幾篇開箱文就狗衝。<br />\n<br />\n講講對呢個制既個人意見，因為我係使用上遇到幾個問題。<br />\n<br />\n最大問題係十字鍵硬撚到仆街，個人感覺300g都黎，點解佢唔做到好似4個主制咁用類似mouse嗰種微動開關？<br />\n<br />\n另外係佢個耳機插口好多本身原裝制用到既耳機都用唔到，包括我新買既Steelseries arctis 7，更新左1.11版後用得翻，但個收音嘜收音超差(插原裝手制收音好好)。<br />\n<br />\n家陣用到好嬲，又唔想賣翻出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望佢會有更新解決個嘜既問題。"},{"pid":"589f5cfe59b57903e812e7093f124a5c56e27cfb","tid":573101,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T06:51:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5af7851feb9fc6ac2cbbfb76049b4e826d4a956","tid":573101,"uid":74044,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T06:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇壞右？</blockquote><br />\n睇過右既問題，詳細測試後結論，更新1.11後就無事。"},{"pid":"360bec6a500fa70a970e8f728ef5eb246a84eb0f","tid":573101,"uid":13843,"like":38,"dislike":6,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"買Razor咁睇唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔去舖試左先？<br />\n<br />\n利申：未試過"},{"pid":"6d9c66a48b3885a9fd017e4c9dd10c46feba673d","tid":573101,"uid":21423,"like":15,"dislike":10,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:34:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78099d8ba2b2c7073fbca0af140228084839d94d","tid":573101,"uid":77769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6d9c66a48b3885a9fd017e4c9dd10c46feba673d","tid":573101,"uid":21423,"like":15,"dislike":10,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"360bec6a500fa70a970e8f728ef5eb246a84eb0f","tid":573101,"uid":13843,"like":38,"dislike":6,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"買Razor咁睇唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔去舖試左先？<br />\n<br />\n利申：未試過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:34:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:35:04.000Z","msg":"都要記得試埋上同下，前同後"},{"pid":"adbf6caf87161844ea8b85e87eb8a564add11cfc","tid":573101,"uid":31306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:35:23.000Z","msg":"有冇人買左nacron第二代？"},{"pid":"a006ae0a33abeb7dfbc615741d71784293f300d6","tid":573101,"uid":1255,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"360bec6a500fa70a970e8f728ef5eb246a84eb0f","tid":573101,"uid":13843,"like":38,"dislike":6,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"買Razor咁睇唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔去舖試左先？<br />\n<br />\n利申：未試過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:36:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 BAM鳩咗個肥C去啦<br />\n成萬5人投咗BAM鳩佢"},{"pid":"0396a8aaff0fafc72efab3e8aecffbfeca7ed696","tid":573101,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"Razer 只可以買DA ，其他好撚廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83120693d6a1e2c68fa7709422d6aacc635e08c7","tid":573101,"uid":74044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買Razor咁睇唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔去舖試左先？<br />\n<br />\n利申：未試過</blockquote><br />\n無鋪頭show個制出黎俾我試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n澳門巴"},{"pid":"79d2a1ac1ed87ebab0db6fff9d0b4eeb373ba7f0","tid":573101,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:39:23.000Z","msg":"剩係佢d制的的聲已經頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78f3147f3231534b61f08327885d7794cb68b0a","tid":573101,"uid":109780,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"360bec6a500fa70a970e8f728ef5eb246a84eb0f","tid":573101,"uid":13843,"like":38,"dislike":6,"score":32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"買Razor咁睇唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔去舖試左先？<br />\n<br />\n利申：未試過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"admin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快啲ban左肥絲佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nban撚埋右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6967682e0710ae2dcd7d9f172f717eb186a58d9f","tid":573101,"uid":74044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:44:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人買左nacron第二代？</blockquote><br />\n我有考慮過，但係1黎自定義我用唔著，2黎唔鐘意蘑菇位到轉<br />\n不過轉左用type C頭比較方便<br />\nrazer用micro usb頭，插口位特殊，原廠線3米太長唔想用，我隨便搵條線批爛個頭就插到入去"},{"pid":"dfa01d3f49e17a21e2cb1adc1974f68b9d2b0b6d","tid":573101,"uid":74044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剩係佢d制的的聲已經頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實用落唔差，開頭我都唔慣，慣左好好用，但擔心耐用度。"},{"pid":"fc6f98e010e255a73f3d239a7ca9e8a75a01ad6b","tid":573101,"uid":32057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfa01d3f49e17a21e2cb1adc1974f68b9d2b0b6d","tid":573101,"uid":74044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剩係佢d制的的聲已經頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實用落唔差，開頭我都唔慣，慣左好好用，但擔心耐用度。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:54:39.000Z","msg":"我用左1年多d 個L3 用左1個月已經有怪聲 唔順卡卡地個d聲"},{"pid":"caa2ab3498f4eca9e02657155797cf0ff61dc9d8","tid":573101,"uid":74044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T08:16:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>剩